[assistant] Fixed the failing test by using Kryo’s public object read/write flow for the read path:
[assistant] 
[assistant] - `kryo.writeObject(output, original, serializer)`
[assistant] - `kryo.readObject(input, arrayType, serializer)`
[assistant] 
